<h2 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-Overview">Overview=
</h2>
<p>This guide covers building, deploying, and using the Nexus File Transfer=
 APIs (v4.1).</p>
<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li>File Upload (client-streaming gRPC)</li>
 <li>File Download (server-streaming gRPC)</li>
 <li>File size limit: 1GB</li>
 <li>Chunk size: 4MB</li>
 <li>Storage location: /home/nutanix/Downloads (on PC)</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-GettingStarted">Ge=
tting Started</h2>
<p><strong>IMPORTANT - Certificate Setup (Do This First!):</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li>Before cloning repositories or building anything, you must install cer=
tificates to access GitHub and Caneveral on Mac.</li>
 <li>This prevents PKXI failure errors during Maven builds.</li>
 <li>Follow: <a href=3D"https://confluence.eng.nutanix.com:8443/spaces/AI/p=
ages/92015216/Install+Certificates+to+access+Github+and+Caneveral+on+Mac" r=
el=3D"nofollow">Install Certificates to access Github and Caneveral on Mac<=
/a></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-CloneRepositories"=
>Clone Repositories</h3>
<p>After installing certificates, clone all repositories to your local mach=
ine:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: bash; gutter: false"># Create a workspace directory
mkdir -p ~/nexus_temp
cd ~/nexus_temp

# Clone ntnx-api-golang-nexus-pc (API definitions and code generation)
git clone https://github.com/nitinmangotra1212/ntnx-api-golang-nexus-pc.git

# Clone ntnx-api-golang-nexus (Go service implementation)
git clone https://github.com/nitinmangotra1212/ntnx-api-golang-nexus.git

# Clone ntnx-api-prism-service (Adonis - REST-to-gRPC gateway)
git clone https://github.com/nutanix-core/ntnx-api-prism-service.git

# Clone ntnx-api-utils-go (Go utilities and dependencies)
git clone https://github.com/nutanix-core/ntnx-api-utils-go.git
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><strong>Repository Structure:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: java; gutter: false">~/nexus_temp/
=E2=94=9C=E2=94=80=E2=94=80 ntnx-api-golang-nexus-pc/     # API definitions=
, code generation
=E2=94=9C=E2=94=80=E2=94=80 ntnx-api-golang-nexus/        # Go service impl=
ementation
=E2=94=9C=E2=94=80=E2=94=80 ntnx-api-prism-service/       # Adonis (REST-to=
-gRPC gateway)
=E2=94=94=E2=94=80=E2=94=80 ntnx-api-utils-go/            # Go utilities an=
d dependencies
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><strong>Repository Links:</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li><strong>ntnx-api-golang-nexus-pc</strong>: <a href=3D"https://github.c=
om/nitinmangotra1212/ntnx-api-golang-nexus-pc.git" class=3D"external-link" =
rel=3D"nofollow">https://github.com/nitinmangotra1212/ntnx-api-golang-nexus=
-pc.git</a></li>
 <li><strong>ntnx-api-golang-nexus</strong>: <a href=3D"https://github.com/=
nitinmangotra1212/ntnx-api-golang-nexus.git" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D=
"nofollow">https://github.com/nitinmangotra1212/ntnx-api-golang-nexus.git</=
a></li>
 <li><strong>ntnx-api-prism-service</strong>: <a href=3D"https://github.com=
/nutanix-core/ntnx-api-prism-service.git" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"no=
follow">https://github.com/nutanix-core/ntnx-api-prism-service.git</a></li>
 <li><strong>ntnx-api-utils-go</strong>: <a href=3D"https://github.com/nuta=
nix-core/ntnx-api-utils-go.git" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">ht=
tps://github.com/nutanix-core/ntnx-api-utils-go.git</a></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-BuildSteps">Build =
Steps</h2>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-Prerequisites">Pre=
requisites</h3>
<p><strong>IMPORTANT - Do This First:</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li><strong>Install Certificates on Mac:</strong> Before starting any buil=
d, you must install certificates to access GitHub and Caneveral on Mac. Thi=
s is required to avoid PKXI failure errors during Maven builds.=20
  <ul>
   <li>Follow the guide: <a href=3D"https://confluence.eng.nutanix.com:8443=
/spaces/AI/pages/92015216/Install+Certificates+to+access+Github+and+Canever=
al+on+Mac" rel=3D"nofollow">Install Certificates to access Github and Canev=
eral on Mac</a></li>
  </ul></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Required Software:</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li>Java 21+</li>
 <li>Go 1.21+</li>
 <li>Maven 3.6+</li>
 <li>Git</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Required Repositories:</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li><code>ntnx-api-golang-nexus-pc</code> - Cloned (see Getting Started se=
ction above)</li>
 <li><code>ntnx-api-golang-nexus</code> - Cloned (see Getting Started secti=
on above)</li>
 <li><code>ntnx-api-prism-service</code> - Cloned (see Getting Started sect=
ion above) - for building Adonis</li>
 <li><code>ntnx-api-utils-go</code> - Cloned (see Getting Started section a=
bove) - for Go service dependencies</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Configuration Files:</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li><code>settings.xml</code> in both Maven projects (included in reposito=
ries)</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Network Access:</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li>Access to Nutanix internal Maven repositories (via VPN or network)</li=
>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-AdonisConfiguratio=
n(BeforeBuild)">Adonis Configuration (Before Build)</h2>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-1.Updateapplicatio=
n.yaml(Local)">1. Update application.yaml (Local)</h3>
<p><strong>File:</strong> <code>ntnx-api-prism-service/src/main/resources/a=
pplication.yaml</code></p>
<p>Ensure these controller packages are included:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: yaml; gutter: false">adonis:
  controller:
    packages:
      onprem:=20
        # ... existing packages ...,
        nexus.v4.server.configuration,
        nexus.v4.config.server.controllers,
        nexus.v4.config.server.services
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><strong>Also verify gRPC configuration:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: yaml; gutter: false">grpc:
  golangnexus:
    host: localhost
    port: 9090
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-2.Updatepom.xmlPro=
pertiesandControllerVersion">2. Update pom.xml Properties and Controller Ve=
rsion</h3>
<p><strong>File:</strong> <code>ntnx-api-prism-service/pom.xml</code></p>
<p><strong>Step 1: Add version property (around line 90):</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: xml; gutter: false">&lt;properties&gt;
  &lt;!-- ... existing properties ... --&gt;
  &lt;golang-nexus-api-controller.version&gt;17.0.0-SNAPSHOT&lt;/golang-nex=
us-api-controller.version&gt;
  &lt;!-- ... other properties ... --&gt;
&lt;/properties&gt;
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><strong>Step 2: Add controller version mapping (around line 1344):</stro=
ng></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: xml; gutter: false">&lt;controller.golang-nexus.version&gt;${golang-nex=
us-api-controller.version}&lt;/controller.golang-nexus.version&gt;
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> This should be added in the <code>&lt;controllerV=
ersions&gt;</code> section along with other controller versions.</p>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-3.VerifyDependenci=
esinpom.xml">3. Verify Dependencies in pom.xml</h3>
<p><strong>File:</strong> <code>ntnx-api-prism-service/pom.xml</code></p>
<p>Ensure these dependencies are present (around line 983):</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: xml; gutter: false">&lt;!-- Golang Nexus Spring MVC Interfaces (needed =
for ItemApiControllerInterface) --&gt;
&lt;dependency&gt;
  &lt;groupId&gt;com.nutanix.nutanix-core.ntnx-api.golang-nexus-pc&lt;/grou=
pId&gt;
  &lt;artifactId&gt;golang-nexus-springmvc-interfaces&lt;/artifactId&gt;
  &lt;version&gt;${golang-nexus-api-controller.version}&lt;/version&gt;
  &lt;exclusions&gt;
    &lt;exclusion&gt;
      &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-webmvc&lt;/artifactId&gt;
      &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework&lt;/groupId&gt;
    &lt;/exclusion&gt;
  &lt;/exclusions&gt;
&lt;/dependency&gt;

&lt;!-- Golang Nexus Protobuf Mappers (needed for ListItemsApiResponseMappe=
r) --&gt;
&lt;dependency&gt;
  &lt;groupId&gt;com.nutanix.nutanix-core.ntnx-api.golang-nexus-pc&lt;/grou=
pId&gt;
  &lt;artifactId&gt;golang-nexus-protobuf-mappers&lt;/artifactId&gt;
  &lt;version&gt;${golang-nexus-api-controller.version}&lt;/version&gt;
  &lt;exclusions&gt;
    &lt;exclusion&gt;
      &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-webmvc&lt;/artifactId&gt;
      &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework&lt;/groupId&gt;
    &lt;/exclusion&gt;
  &lt;/exclusions&gt;
&lt;/dependency&gt;

&lt;!-- Golang Nexus gRPC Client --&gt;
&lt;dependency&gt;
  &lt;groupId&gt;com.nutanix.nutanix-core.ntnx-api.golang-nexus-pc&lt;/grou=
pId&gt;
  &lt;artifactId&gt;golang-nexus-grpc-client&lt;/artifactId&gt;
  &lt;version&gt;${golang-nexus-api-controller.version}&lt;/version&gt;
  &lt;exclusions&gt;
    &lt;exclusion&gt;
      &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-webmvc&lt;/artifactId&gt;
      &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework&lt;/groupId&gt;
    &lt;/exclusion&gt;
  &lt;/exclusions&gt;
&lt;/dependency&gt;
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><strong>All three dependencies are required.</strong> Missing any one wi=
ll cause Adonis to fail to start.</p>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-1.Buildntnx-api-go=
lang-nexus-pc(GeneratesAPIartifacts)">1. Build ntnx-api-golang-nexus-pc (Ge=
nerates API artifacts)</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: bash; gutter: false"># Navigate to the cloned repository
cd ~/nexus_temp/ntnx-api-golang-nexus-pc

# Export MAVEN_OPTS to fix Java module access issues (required for Java 21)
export MAVEN_OPTS=3D"--add-opens java.base/java.lang=3DALL-UNNAMED --add-op=
ens java.base/java.lang.reflect=3DALL-UNNAMED --add-opens java.base/java.ut=
il=3DALL-UNNAMED"

# Build with Maven
mvn clean install -DskipTests -s settings.xml
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> The <code>MAVEN_OPTS</code> export is required to=
 fix Java 21 module access issues. If you get errors like <code>"module jav=
a.base does not 'opens java.lang' to unnamed module"</code>, make sure you'=
ve exported <code>MAVEN_OPTS</code> before running the build.</p>
<p><strong>What it generates:</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li>API YAML artifacts</li>
 <li>Proto files (<code>file_service.proto</code>)</li>
 <li>Java client classes (<code>NexusConfigFileController.java</code>, <cod=
e>NexusConfigFileServiceImpl.java</code>)</li>
 <li>Go DTOs and protobuf code</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Expected output:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: java; gutter: false">[INFO] BUILD SUCCESS
[INFO] Total time:  XX.XXX s
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><strong>Generated artifacts:</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li><code>target/generated-api-artifacts/</code> - API definitions</li>
 <li><code>generated-code/protobuf/nexus/v4/config/file_service.proto</code=
></li>
 <li><code>golang-nexus-api-codegen/golang-nexus-grpc-client/target/golang-=
nexus-grpc-client-17.0.0-SNAPSHOT.jar</code></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-2.BuildGoService(R=
equiresstep1tocompletefirst)">2. Build Go Service (Requires step 1 to compl=
ete first)</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: bash; gutter: false"># Navigate to the cloned repository
cd ~/nexus_temp/ntnx-api-golang-nexus

# Build Linux binary
GOOS=3Dlinux GOARCH=3Damd64 go build -o golang-linux-final golang-nexus-ser=
vice/server/main.go
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><strong>What it creates:</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li>Linux binary: <code>golang-linux-final</code></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Expected output:</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li>No errors, binary created successfully</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-3.Buildprism-servi=
ce(Requiresstep1tocompletefirst)">3. Build prism-service (Requires step 1 t=
o complete first)</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: bash; gutter: false">cd ~/ntnx-api-prism-service

# Export MAVEN_OPTS to fix Java module access issues (required for Java 21)
export MAVEN_OPTS=3D"--add-opens java.base/java.lang=3DALL-UNNAMED --add-op=
ens java.base/java.lang.reflect=3DALL-UNNAMED --add-opens java.base/java.ut=
il=3DALL-UNNAMED"

# Build Adonis
mvn clean install -DskipTests -s settings.xml
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><strong>What it creates:</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li><code>target/prism-service-17.6.0-SNAPSHOT.jar</code> (includes nexus =
file transfer code)</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Expected output:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: java; gutter: false">[INFO] BUILD SUCCESS
[INFO] Total time:  XX.XXX s
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<hr>
<h2 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-DeploymentSteps(On=
PC)">Deployment Steps (On PC)</h2>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-PrerequisitesonPC"=
>Prerequisites on PC</h3>
<ul>
 <li>Prism Central VM access</li>
 <li>SSH access to PC (<code>nutanix@10.124.86.254</code>)</li>
 <li>IDF service running on PC</li>
 <li>Adonis service directory: <code>~/adonis/</code></li>
 <li>API artifacts directory: <code>~/api_artifacts/</code></li>
 <li>Mercury configuration directory: <code>~/config/mercury/</code></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-Step1:DeployGoServ=
ice">Step 1: Deploy Go Service</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: bash; gutter: false">PC_IP=3D"10.124.86.254"

# Create directory on PC
ssh nutanix@${PC_IP} "mkdir -p ~/golang-nexus-build"

# From local machine - Copy binary
scp -O ~/nexus_temp/ntnx-api-golang-nexus/golang-linux-final \
    nutanix@${PC_IP}:~/golang-nexus-build/golang-nexus-server

# On PC, make executable and start
ssh nutanix@${PC_IP}
cd ~/golang-nexus-build
chmod +x golang-nexus-server
nohup ./golang-nexus-server &gt; golang_nexus.log 2&gt;&amp;1 &amp;
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> Logs are written to <code>~/golang-nexus-build/go=
lang_nexus.log</code>. The service will continue running even after you dis=
connect from SSH.</p>
<p><strong>Verify Go service is running:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: bash; gutter: false"># On PC
ps aux | grep golang-nexus-server | grep -v grep
# Should show process listening on port 9090
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-Step2:DeployAPIArt=
ifacts">Step 2: Deploy API Artifacts</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: bash; gutter: false">PC_IP=3D"10.124.86.254"

# Create directory structure on PC
ssh nutanix@${PC_IP} "mkdir -p ~/api_artifacts/nexus/v4.r1.a1/golang-nexus-=
api-definitions-17.0.0-SNAPSHOT"

# From local machine - Copy artifacts
scp -r -O ~/nexus_temp/ntnx-api-golang-nexus-pc/golang-nexus-api-definition=
s/target/generated-api-artifacts/* \
    nutanix@${PC_IP}:~/api_artifacts/nexus/v4.r1.a1/golang-nexus-api-defini=
tions-17.0.0-SNAPSHOT/
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><strong>Verify artifacts include:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: bash; gutter: false"># On PC
ssh nutanix@${PC_IP}
ls -la ~/api_artifacts/nexus/v4.r1.a1/golang-nexus-api-definitions-17.0.0-S=
NAPSHOT/
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><strong>Should contain:</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li><code>swagger-all-17.0.0-SNAPSHOT.yaml</code></li>
 <li><code>*.proto</code> files (e.g., <code>config.proto</code>, <code>ite=
m_service.proto</code>, <code>file_service.proto</code>)</li>
 <li><code>api-manifest-17.0.0-SNAPSHOT.json</code></li>
 <li><code>object-type-mapping-17.0.0-SNAPSHOT.yaml</code></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-Step3:Updatelookup=
_cache.jsononPC">Step 3: Update lookup_cache.json on PC</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: bash; gutter: false">PC_IP=3D"10.124.86.254"
ssh nutanix@${PC_IP}

# Backup existing file
cp ~/api_artifacts/lookup_cache.json ~/api_artifacts/lookup_cache.json.back=
up

# Edit file (use vi/nano)
vi ~/api_artifacts/lookup_cache.json
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><strong>Add entry in <code>routeMappings</code> array:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: json; gutter: false">{
  "routeMappings": [
    // ... existing entries ...,
    {
      "apiPath": "/nexus/v4.1/config",
      "artifactPath": "nexus/v4.r1.a1/golang-nexus-api-definitions-17.0.0-S=
NAPSHOT"
    }
  ]
}
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-Step4:CreateMercur=
yConfigurationonPC">Step 4: Create Mercury Configuration on PC</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: bash; gutter: false">PC_IP=3D"10.124.86.254"
ssh nutanix@${PC_IP}

# Create directory
mkdir -p ~/config/mercury

# Create config file
cat &gt; ~/config/mercury/mercury_request_handler_config_golangnexus.json &=
lt;&lt; 'EOF'
{
  "api_path_config_list" : [
    {
      "api_path" : "/api/nexus/v4.1",
      "handler_list" : [
        {
          "priority" : 1,
          "port" : 8888,
          "transport_options" : "kHttp",
          "external_request_auth_options" : "kAllowAnyAuthenticatedUserExt"=
,
          "internal_request_auth_options" : "kAllowAnyAuthenticatedUserInt"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "api_path" : "/api/nexus/unversioned",
      "handler_list" : [
        {
          "priority" : 1,
          "port" : 8888,
          "transport_options" : "kHttp",
          "external_request_auth_options" : "kAllowAnyAuthenticatedUserExt"=
,
          "internal_request_auth_options" : "kAllowAnyAuthenticatedUserInt"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
EOF
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><strong>Verify Mercury config:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: bash; gutter: false"># On PC
cat ~/config/mercury/mercury_request_handler_config_golangnexus.json
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-Step5:Deployprism-=
serviceJAR">Step 5: Deploy prism-service JAR</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: bash; gutter: false">PC_IP=3D"10.124.86.254"

# Stop Adonis first (on PC)
ssh nutanix@${PC_IP} "genesis stop adonis mercury"
sleep 10

# Remove backup JARs (if any)
ssh nutanix@${PC_IP} "rm -f ~/adonis/lib/*-BACKUP-*.jar"

# From local machine - Copy new JAR
scp -O ~/ntnx-api-prism-service/target/prism-service-17.6.0-SNAPSHOT.jar \
    nutanix@${PC_IP}:~/adonis/lib/

# Verify only SNAPSHOT JAR exists
ssh nutanix@${PC_IP} "ls -lh ~/adonis/lib/prism-service-*.jar"
# Should show only: prism-service-17.6.0-SNAPSHOT.jar
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-Step6:Updateapplic=
ation.yamlonPC">Step 6: Update application.yaml on PC</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: bash; gutter: false">PC_IP=3D"10.124.86.254"
ssh nutanix@${PC_IP}

# Backup existing file
cp ~/adonis/config/application.yaml ~/adonis/config/application.yaml.backup

# Edit file (use vi/nano)
vi ~/adonis/config/application.yaml
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><strong>Ensure these packages are in <code>controller.packages</code>:</=
strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: yaml; gutter: false">adonis:
  controller:
    packages:
      onprem:=20
        # ... existing packages ...,
        nexus.v4.server.configuration,
        nexus.v4.config.server.controllers,
        nexus.v4.config.server.services
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><strong>Also verify gRPC configuration:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: yaml; gutter: false">grpc:
  golangnexus:
    host: localhost
    port: 9090
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-Step7:RegisterIDFE=
ntityTypes(One-timesetup)">Step 7: Register IDF Entity Types (One-time setu=
p)</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: bash; gutter: false">PC_IP=3D"10.124.86.254"

# From local machine - Copy setup script
scp -O ~/nexus_temp/ntnx-api-golang-nexus-pc/setup_nexus_idf.py \
    nutanix@${PC_IP}:~/ntnx-api-golang-nexus-pc/

# On PC - Run setup script
ssh nutanix@${PC_IP}
cd ~/ntnx-api-golang-nexus-pc
python3 setup_nexus_idf.py
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><strong>This registers:</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li><code>item</code> entity type (if not already registered)</li>
 <li><code>file</code> entity type (for file metadata)</li>
 <li>Associated attributes (<code>ext_id</code>, <code>file_name</code>, <c=
ode>file_size</code>, <code>content_type</code>)</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Expected output:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: java; gutter: false">=E2=9C=85 Successfully registered entity type: fil=
e
=E2=9C=85 Successfully registered metric types (attributes) for file
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><strong>Optional - Copy list_files.py utility:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: bash; gutter: false"># From local machine
scp -O ~/nexus_temp/ntnx-api-golang-nexus-pc/list_files.py \
    nutanix@${PC_IP}:~/ntnx-api-golang-nexus-pc/

# On PC - Use to view uploaded files
ssh nutanix@${PC_IP}
cd ~/ntnx-api-golang-nexus-pc
python3 list_files.py
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-Step8:StartService=
sonPC">Step 8: Start Services on PC</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: bash; gutter: false">PC_IP=3D"10.124.86.254"
ssh nutanix@${PC_IP}

# Start Go service (if not already running)
cd ~/golang-nexus-build
nohup ./golang-nexus-server &gt; golang_nexus.log 2&gt;&amp;1 &amp;

# Start Adonis
cluster start
sleep 30

# Check status
genesis status adonis
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-Step9:VerifyDeploy=
ment">Step 9: Verify Deployment</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: bash; gutter: false">PC_IP=3D"10.124.86.254"
ssh nutanix@${PC_IP}

# 1. Check Adonis logs for controller registration
tail -100 ~/adonis/logs/prism-service.log | grep -i "nexus\|controller" | t=
ail -10

# 2. Check Go service is running
ps aux | grep golang-nexus-server | grep -v grep

# 3. Test API endpoint (Items endpoint)
curl -k https://127.0.0.1:9440/api/nexus/v4.1/config/items -u 'admin:Nutani=
x.123'

# 4. Check Go service logs
tail -f ~/golang-nexus-build/golang_nexus.log

# 5. Check Adonis logs
tail -f ~/adonis/logs/prism-service.log
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><strong>Look for:</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li>Go service: <code>Starting Golang Nexus gRPC server on :9090</code></l=
i>
 <li>Adonis: No errors related to nexus file endpoints</li>
 <li>Controller registration: <code>nexus.v4.config.server.controllers</cod=
e> packages loaded</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-APIEndpoints">API =
Endpoints</h2>
