/h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: java; gutter: false">https://10.124.86.254:9440/api/nexus/v4.1/config
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-1.UploadFile">1. U=
pload File</h3>
<p><strong>Endpoint:</strong> <code>POST /upload</code></p>
<p><strong>URL:</strong> <code><span class=3D"nobr"><a class=3D"external-li=
nk" href=3D"https://10.124.86.254:9440/api/nexus/v4.1/config/upload" rel=3D=
"nofollow">https://10.124.86.254:9440/api/nexus/v4.1/config/upload<sup><img=
 class=3D"rendericon" src=3D"692461dfa2b119cdcab7a03ec1f332857f87a13a06a0dc=
c3029533cd51cb971f" height=3D"7" width=3D"7" align=3D"absmiddle" alt=3D"" b=
order=3D"0"></sup></a></span></code></p>
<p><strong>Headers:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: java; gutter: false">Content-Type: application/octet-stream
Content-Length: &lt;file_size_in_bytes&gt;
Content-Disposition: attachment;filename=3D&lt;filename&gt;
Authorization: Basic &lt;base64_credentials&gt;
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><strong>Request Body:</strong> Binary file data</p>
<p><strong>Response:</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li><strong>Status:</strong> <code>201 Created</code> (Success) / <code>50=
0 Internal Server Error</code> (Error)</li>
 <li><strong>Body:</strong> JSON with file metadata containing:=20
  <ul>
   <li><code>extId</code> - External ID of the resource created (UUID)</li>
   <li><code>fileName</code> - Original filename</li>
   <li><code>fileSize</code> - File size in bytes</li>
   <li><code>contentType</code> - MIME type of the file</li>
   <li><code>$reserved</code> - Reserved fields (e.g., <code>$fv: "v4.r1"</=
code>)</li>
   <li><code>$objectType</code> - Object type (e.g., <code>"nexus.v4.config=
.File"</code>)</li>
  </ul></li>
</ul>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: json; gutter: false">{
  "extId": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-1234-567890abcdef",
  "fileName": "example.mov",
  "fileSize": 10406068,
  "contentType": "application/octet-stream",
  "$reserved": {
    "$fv": "v4.r1"
  },
  "$objectType": "nexus.v4.config.File"
}
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<ul>
 <li><strong>Response Headers:</strong>
  <ul>
   <li><code>Location</code> - URL header of newly created resource (e.g., =
<code>/nexus/v4.1/config/download/<a class=3D"createlink" href=3D"/pages/cr=
eatepage.action?spaceKey=3D~nitin.mangotra&amp;title=3DextId&amp;linkCreati=
on=3Dtrue&amp;fromPageId=3D500182886&amp;atl_token=3D3a1ca189758763d7398afb=
796a4ba02d63a67def">extId</a></code>)</li>
  </ul></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Response Requirements (as per code reference):</strong></p>
<ol>
 <li><code>201 Success</code> / <code>500 Error</code> status code</li>
 <li><code>extId</code> of the resource created (in response body)</li>
 <li><code>Location</code> URL header of newly created resource</li>
</ol>
<p><strong>Example (curl):</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: bash; gutter: false">curl -k -X POST \
  https://10.124.86.254:9440/api/nexus/v4.1/config/upload \
  --data-binary @/path/to/file.mov \
  -u 'admin:Nutanix.123' \
  -H 'Content-Type: application/octet-stream' \
  -H 'Content-Length: 10406068' \
  -H 'Content-Disposition: attachment;filename=3Dfile.mov'
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><strong>File Storage:</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li>Files are saved to: <code>/home/nutanix/Downloads/<a class=3D"createli=
nk" href=3D"/pages/createpage.action?spaceKey=3D~nitin.mangotra&amp;title=
=3DextId&amp;linkCreation=3Dtrue&amp;fromPageId=3D500182886&amp;atl_token=
=3D3a1ca189758763d7398afb796a4ba02d63a67def">extId</a></code></li>
 <li>Metadata is stored in IDF (Insights Data Framework)</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Limits:</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li>Maximum file size: 1GB</li>
 <li>Chunk size: 4MB</li>
 <li>Supported formats: Any binary file (txt, mov, zip, tar, etc.)</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-2.DownloadFile">2.=
 Download File</h3>
<p><strong>Endpoint:</strong> <code>GET /download/<a class=3D"createlink" h=
ref=3D"/pages/createpage.action?spaceKey=3D~nitin.mangotra&amp;title=3DextI=
d&amp;linkCreation=3Dtrue&amp;fromPageId=3D500182886&amp;atl_token=3D3a1ca1=
89758763d7398afb796a4ba02d63a67def">extId</a></code></p>
<p><strong>URL:</strong> <code><span class=3D"nobr"><a class=3D"external-li=
nk" href=3D"https://10.124.86.254:9440/api/nexus/v4.1/config/download/%3Cac=
%3Alink%3E%3Cri%3Apage+ri%3Acontent-title%3D%22extId%22+%2F%3E%3C%2Fac%3Ali=
nk%3E" rel=3D"nofollow">https://10.124.86.254:9440/api/nexus/v4.1/config/do=
wnload/</a><a class=3D"createlink" href=3D"/pages/createpage.action?spaceKe=
y=3D~nitin.mangotra&amp;title=3DextId&amp;linkCreation=3Dtrue&amp;fromPageI=
d=3D500182886&amp;atl_token=3D3a1ca189758763d7398afb796a4ba02d63a67def">ext=
Id</a><sup><img class=3D"rendericon" src=3D"692461dfa2b119cdcab7a03ec1f3328=
57f87a13a06a0dcc3029533cd51cb971f" height=3D"7" width=3D"7" align=3D"absmid=
dle" alt=3D"" border=3D"0"></sup></span></code></p>
<p><strong>Path Parameters:</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li><code>extId</code> (required): External ID of the file (UUID format)</=
li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Headers:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: java; gutter: false">Authorization: Basic &lt;base64_credentials&gt;
Accept: application/octet-stream
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><strong>Response:</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li><strong>Status:</strong> <code>200 OK</code></li>
 <li><strong>Body:</strong> Binary file data (streamed)</li>
 <li><strong>Headers:</strong>
  <ul>
   <li><code>Content-Type: application/octet-stream</code></li>
   <li><code>Content-Length: &lt;file_size_in_bytes&gt;</code></li>
   <li><code>Content-Disposition: attachment;filename=3D&lt;original_filena=
me&gt;</code></li>
  </ul></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Example (curl):</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: bash; gutter: false">curl -k -X GET \
  'https://10.124.86.254:9440/api/nexus/v4.1/config/download/a1b2c3d4-e5f6-=
7890-1234-567890abcdef' \
  -u 'admin:Nutanix.123' \
  -H 'Accept: application/octet-stream' \
  -o downloaded_file.mov
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><strong>File Retrieval:</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li>First attempts to get metadata from IDF</li>
 <li>Falls back to filesystem if IDF metadata not found</li>
 <li>Files are read from: <code>/home/nutanix/Downloads/<a class=3D"createl=
ink" href=3D"/pages/createpage.action?spaceKey=3D~nitin.mangotra&amp;title=
=3DextId&amp;linkCreation=3Dtrue&amp;fromPageId=3D500182886&amp;atl_token=
=3D3a1ca189758763d7398afb796a4ba02d63a67def">extId</a></code></li>
</ul>
