<hr>
<h2 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-Troubleshooting">T=
roubleshooting</h2>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-Issue:Uploadreturn=
s503">Issue: Upload returns 503</h3>
<p><strong>Possible causes:</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li>Go service not running</li>
 <li>Adonis not restarted after deploying new JAR</li>
 <li>API artifacts not deployed</li>
 <li>Mercury config missing</li>
 <li>lookup_cache.json not updated</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Solution:</strong></p>
<ol>
 <li>Check Go service: <code>ps aux | grep golang-nexus-server | grep -v gr=
ep</code></li>
 <li>Verify Mercury config: <code>cat ~/config/mercury/mercury_request_hand=
ler_config_golangnexus.json</code></li>
 <li>Verify lookup_cache.json: <code>grep -i nexus ~/api_artifacts/lookup_c=
ache.json</code></li>
 <li>Restart Adonis: <code>genesis stop adonis mercury &amp;&amp; cluster s=
tart</code></li>
 <li>Verify API artifacts: <code>ls ~/api_artifacts/nexus/v4.r1.a1/</code><=
/li>
</ol>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-Issue:Downloadretu=
rns500">Issue: Download returns 500</h3>
<p><strong>Possible causes:</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li>File not found in filesystem</li>
 <li>IDF entity type not registered</li>
 <li>File metadata missing in IDF</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Solution:</strong></p>
<ol>
 <li>Check file exists: <code>ls -lh /home/nutanix/Downloads/<a class=3D"cr=
eatelink" href=3D"/pages/createpage.action?spaceKey=3D~nitin.mangotra&amp;t=
itle=3DextId&amp;linkCreation=3Dtrue&amp;fromPageId=3D500182886&amp;atl_tok=
en=3D3a1ca189758763d7398afb796a4ba02d63a67def">extId</a></code></li>
 <li>Register IDF: <code>python3 ~/ntnx-api-golang-nexus-pc/setup_nexus_idf=
.py</code></li>
 <li>Check Go service logs: <code>tail -f ~/golang-nexus-build/golang_nexus=
.log</code></li>
 <li>Check Adonis logs: <code>tail -f ~/adonis/logs/prism-service.log | gre=
p -i error</code></li>
</ol>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-Issue:Partialfiled=
ownload(100MBinsteadof210MB)">Issue: Partial file download (100MB instead o=
f 210MB)</h3>
<p><strong>Possible causes:</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li>gRPC timeout too short (30 seconds default)</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Solution:</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li>Increase timeout in <code>application.yaml</code> on PC:</li>
</ul>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: yaml; gutter: false">grpc:
  file:
    stream:
      timeout: 300  # 5 minutes
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<ul>
 <li>Restart Adonis after changing configuration</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-Issue:Buildfailswi=
th&quot;cannotfindsymbol&quot;">Issue: Build fails with "cannot find symbol=
"</h3>
<p><strong>Possible causes:</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li>Missing <code>dev-platform-java-models</code> dependency</li>
 <li>Fix scripts not running</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Solution:</strong></p>
<ol>
 <li>Verify <code>pom.xml</code> has <code>dev-platform-java-models</code> =
dependency</li>
 <li>Check fix scripts exist: <code>ls scripts/fix-file-*.sh</code></li>
 <li>Rebuild: <code>mvn clean install -DskipTests -s settings.xml</code></l=
i>
</ol>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-Issue:AdonisUsingB=
ackupJAR">Issue: Adonis Using Backup JAR</h3>
<p><strong>Symptom:</strong> Adonis is using <code>prism-service-<strong><s=
pan style=3D"text-decoration: line-through;">BACKUP</span></strong>.jar</co=
de> instead of SNAPSHOT</p>
<p><strong>Solution:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: bash; gutter: false">PC_IP=3D"10.124.86.254"
ssh nutanix@${PC_IP}
genesis stop adonis mercury
sleep 10
rm -f ~/adonis/lib/*-BACKUP-*.jar
# Or move it: mkdir -p ~/adonis/lib/backup-jars &amp;&amp; mv ~/adonis/lib/=
*-BACKUP-*.jar ~/adonis/lib/backup-jars/
cluster start
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-Issue:Missing.prot=
oFilesinAPIArtifacts">Issue: Missing .proto Files in API Artifacts</h3>
<p><strong>Symptom:</strong> <code>.proto</code> files are missing from <co=
de>api_artifacts</code> directory</p>
<p><strong>Solution:</strong></p>
<ol>
 <li>Check <code>golang-nexus-api-definitions/pom.xml</code> has <code>mave=
n-antrun-plugin</code> to copy <code>.proto</code> files</li>
 <li>Rebuild: <code>mvn clean install -DskipTests -s settings.xml</code></l=
i>
 <li>Verify <code>.proto</code> files are in <code>target/generated-api-art=
ifacts/</code></li>
 <li>Copy artifacts to PC again</li>
</ol>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-Issue:404ErroronAP=
IEndpoint">Issue: 404 Error on API Endpoint</h3>
<p><strong>Checklist:</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li>:tick: Controller in JAR: <code>jar -tf ~/adonis/lib/prism-service-17.=
6.0-SNAPSHOT.jar | grep NexusConfigFileController</code></li>
 <li>:tick: <code>application.yaml</code> has controller packages (<code>ne=
xus.v4.config.server.controllers</code>)</li>
 <li>:tick: <code>lookup_cache.json</code> has API path mapping (<code>/nex=
us/v4.1/config</code>)</li>
 <li>:tick: API artifacts are in correct directory (<code>~/api_artifacts/n=
exus/v4.r1.a1/</code>)</li>
 <li>:tick: Mercury config exists (<code>~/config/mercury/mercury_request_h=
andler_config_golangnexus.json</code>)</li>
 <li>:tick: Adonis restarted after changes</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-Issue:MissingItemA=
piControllerInterfaceorListItemsApiResponseMapper">Issue: Missing ItemApiCo=
ntrollerInterface or ListItemsApiResponseMapper</h3>
<p><strong>Error:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: java; gutter: false">java.io.FileNotFoundException: class path resource=
 [nexus/v4/config/ItemApiControllerInterface.class] cannot be opened
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><strong>Solution:</strong></p>
<ol>
 <li>Ensure dependencies are in Adonis's <code>pom.xml</code>:=20
  <ul>
   <li><code>golang-nexus-springmvc-interfaces</code></li>
   <li><code>golang-nexus-protobuf-mappers</code></li>
   <li><code>golang-nexus-grpc-client</code></li>
  </ul></li>
 <li>Rebuild Adonis: <code>mvn clean install -DskipTests -s settings.xml</c=
ode></li>
 <li>Copy new JAR to PC</li>
 <li>Restart Adonis</li>
</ol>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-VerifyJARContentso=
nPC">Verify JAR Contents on PC</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: bash; gutter: false">PC_IP=3D"10.124.86.254"
ssh nutanix@${PC_IP}

mkdir -p ~/temp
cd ~/temp
rm -rf BOOT-INF 2&gt;/dev/null

# Extract JAR
jar -xf ~/adonis/lib/prism-service-17.6.0-SNAPSHOT.jar BOOT-INF/lib/

# Check interface
jar -tf BOOT-INF/lib/golang-nexus-springmvc-interfaces-17.0.0-SNAPSHOT.jar =
| grep -i "ItemApiControllerInterface"
# Should show: nexus/v4/config/ItemApiControllerInterface.class

# Check mapper
jar -tf BOOT-INF/lib/golang-nexus-protobuf-mappers-17.0.0-SNAPSHOT.jar | gr=
ep -i "ListItemsApiResponseMapper"
# Should show: dp1/mock/nexus/v4/config/mappers/ListItemsApiResponseMapper.=
class

# Check controller
jar -tf BOOT-INF/lib/golang-nexus-grpc-client-17.0.0-SNAPSHOT.jar | grep -i=
 "NexusConfigFileController"
# Should show: nexus/v4/config/server/controllers/NexusConfigFileController=
.class

rm -rf BOOT-INF
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-CheckWhichJARAdoni=
sisUsing">Check Which JAR Adonis is Using</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: bash; gutter: false">PC_IP=3D"10.124.86.254"
ssh nutanix@${PC_IP}
ps aux | grep -i 'prism-service.*jar' | grep -v grep
# Should show: prism-service-17.6.0-SNAPSHOT.jar
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-CheckAdonisLogs">C=
heck Adonis Logs</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: bash; gutter: false">PC_IP=3D"10.124.86.254"
ssh nutanix@${PC_IP}

# Recent errors
tail -100 ~/adonis/logs/prism-service.log | grep -i "error\|exception" | ta=
il -10

# Startup messages
tail -100 ~/adonis/logs/prism-service.log | grep -i "started\|ready" | tail=
 -5

# Controller registration
tail -200 ~/adonis/logs/prism-service.log | grep -i "nexus\|controller" | t=
ail -10
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
