ick Reference</h2>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-BuildOrder">Build =
Order</h3>
<ol>
 <li><code>ntnx-api-golang-nexus-pc</code> (generates code)</li>
 <li><code>ntnx-api-golang-nexus</code> (uses generated code)</li>
 <li><code>ntnx-api-prism-service</code> (uses JARs from step 1)</li>
</ol>
<h3 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-DeploymentOrder">D=
eployment Order</h3>
