 <li>Deploy API artifacts</li>
 <li>Update lookup_cache.json</li>
 <li>Create Mercury config</li>
 <li>Deploy prism-service JAR</li>
 <li>Update application.yaml on PC</li>
 <li>Register IDF entity types</li>
 <li>Start services</li>
 <li>Verify deployment</li>
</ol>
