<h2 id=3D"Build,Deployment&amp;APIGuideNexusFileTransfer-DeploymentChecklis=
t">Deployment Checklist</h2>
<p><strong>Before deploying, ensure:</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li>( ) All three repositories built successfully</li>
 <li>( ) Go service binary created (<code>golang-linux-final</code>)</li>
 <li>( ) API artifacts generated (<code>target/generated-api-artifacts/</co=
de>)</li>
 <li>( ) prism-service JAR includes nexus dependencies</li>
 <li>( ) PC IP address is correct (<code>10.124.86.254</code>)</li>
 <li>( ) SSH access to PC is working</li>
 <li>( ) IDF service is running on PC</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>After deploying, verify:</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li>( ) Go service is running (<code>ps aux | grep golang-nexus-server</co=
de>)</li>
 <li>( ) API artifacts copied to PC</li>
 <li>( ) <code>lookup_cache.json</code> updated with nexus path</li>
 <li>( ) Mercury config file created</li>
 <li>( ) <code>application.yaml</code> has controller packages</li>
 <li>( ) prism-service JAR deployed (SNAPSHOT version)</li>
 <li>( ) IDF entity types registered</li>
 <li>( ) Adonis restarted successfully</li>
 <li>( ) API endpoints responding (test with curl)</li>
</ul>
